{"tid":1354190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨區議員：中聯辦曾籲村民趕暴徒","createTime":"2019-07-23T05:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:14:21.000Z","uid":54921,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5523f525fa8b27ca2ee9c355a871c84b10e95c1e","tid":1354190,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"//<br />\n另外元朗民主黨區議員黃偉賢今日出席now《時事全方位》節目，稱早於7月11日十八鄉鄉事委員會就職典禮上，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中聯辦</span></span></strong>新界工作部部長李薊貽曾上台發言，期間他放下預先準備的講稿，並呼籲愛國愛港的村民不要讓「暴徒」進入元朗搞事，「入來就一定要趕他們走」。黃偉賢形容當日中聯辦發揮動員力後，便出現破壞元朗連儂牆、放映會襲擊等事件。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>先查清</strong></span></span><br />\n//"},{"pid":"7f8ab85d6b689ec025f66b1a96e35758f544f1bb","tid":1354190,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:56:21.000Z","msg":"有無片先？<br />\n<br />\n呢D場合, 應該有錄影"},{"pid":"ffbde912f86da53ffa11d99ca70625c9def89b53","tid":1354190,"uid":203697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:57:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a8c45fb92fa39926cb2c31521062313a2fbbaae6","tid":1354190,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f8ab85d6b689ec025f66b1a96e35758f544f1bb","tid":1354190,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:56:21.000Z","msg":"有無片先？<br />\n<br />\n呢D場合, 應該有錄影"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c17c8105858e53fc68abac88a6a7882bdf1586","tid":1354190,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n共黑合作"},{"pid":"9d3be9faacbeddd0ba72db66fe4751fcae1b0fae","tid":1354190,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f8ab85d6b689ec025f66b1a96e35758f544f1bb","tid":1354190,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime"